cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "gaussian-tools"
abstract: "Python utilities for computational chemists working with Gaussian 
  quantum chemistry calculations. Includes tools for geometry extraction, 
  TD-DFT root tracking, batch GJF generation, and vibrational mode 
  coefficient decomposition."
authors:
